Simulation of breach event counts from Fig.5 of "COVID-19 in low-tolerance border quarantine systems: Impact of the Delta variant of SARS-CoV-2" using Poisson distribution

breach_events.Rd

Simulation of breach event counts from Fig.5 of "COVID-19 in low-tolerance border quarantine systems: Impact of the Delta variant of SARS-CoV-2" using Poisson distribution

Usage

breach_events

Format

A data frame with 84 rows and 4 columns

day

Days infectious in community

panel

  1. A: Ancestral strain without vaccination

  2. B: Ancestral strain with vaccination

  3. C: Delta strain without vaccination

  4. D: Delta strain with vaccination

traveler_count_pois

Traveler breach counts, generated by rpois() function

worker_count_pois

Worker breach counts, generated by rpois() function

Source

https://https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/sciadv.abm3624#F5
